title: The Lord's Prayer
lyrics:
Yours is the kingdom
And the power
And the glory
Forever
Yours is the kingdom

And the power

And the glory

Forever



Father in Heaven

Holy is Your Name

Your kingdom come

Your will be done on earth

As it is in Heaven

Our Father in Heaven



Yours is the kingdom

And the power

And the glory

Forever



Yours is the kingdom

And the power

And the glory

Forever



Give us each moment

All that we need

Forgive us our sins

As we forgive the ones

Who have sinned againts us

Our Father in Heaven



Lead us not into temptation

God deliver us from the enemy



Yours is the kingdom

And the power

And the glory

Forever



Yours is the kingdom

And the power

And the glory

Forever



Our Father have Your way

On the earth

Your will be done

On the earth

Your will be done

On the earth

Your will be done

Forever
